\c 9
\s Jehovha achaparadza marudzi eKenani
\p
\v 1 Inzwa, Israeri; unoyambuka nhasi Joridhani, kupinda ugare nhaka yemarudzi\x + 11.31. 12.10. Josh. 1.11.\x* makuru uye ane simba kukupfuura, maguta makuru\x + 7.1.\x* ane masvingo anosvika kumatenga\x + 1.28.\x*,
\v 2 vanhu vakuru uye varefu, vana veVaAnaki vaunoziva, iwe wakanzwa \add nezvavo zvichinzi\add*: Ndiani angamira pamberi pevana vaAnaki\x + Num. 13.22.\x*?
\v 3 Naizvozvo ziva nhasi kuti Jehovha Mwari wako ndiye anoyambuka mberi kwako, ari\x + 31.3. Josh. 3.11.\x* moto unoparadza\x + 4.24.\x*; iye achavaparadza, uye iye achavaburusira pasi pamberi pako\x + 7.23.\x*; zvino muchavadzinga vabve panhaka yavo, uye muvaparadze nekukurumidza, Jehovha sezvaakataura kwauri\x + Eki. 23.31. Det. 7.24. Eki. 15.9.\x*.
\v 4 Usataura mumoyo mako, Jehovha Mwari wako paavadzinga pamberi pako, uchiti: Nekuda kwekururama kwangu Jehovha wakandipinza kuti ndigare nhaka yenyika ino\x + 8.17.\x*; asi nekuda kwekuipa kwendudzi idzi Jehovha\x + Gen. 15.16. Rev. 18.24,25. Det. 18.12.\x* anovadzinga vabve panhaka yavo pamberi pako\x + Eki. 23.31. Det. 7.24. Eki. 15.9.\x*.
\v 5 Kwete nekuda kwekururama kwako kana nekuda kwekururama kwemoyo wako, unopinda udye nhaka yenyika yawo\x + Tit. 3.5.\x*; asi nekuda kwekuipa kwemarudzi awa Jehovha Mwari wako anoadzinga abve pamberi pako\x + Eki. 23.31. Det. 7.24. Eki. 15.9.\x*, uye kuti asimbise shoko Jehovha raakapikira madzibaba ako, kuna Abhurahama, kuna Isaka, nekuna Jakove\x + Gen.. 50.24.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino ziva, kuti kwete nekuda kwekururama kwako Jehovha Mwari wako anokupa nyika iyi yakanaka kuigara nhaka; nokuti uri rudzi rwune mutsipa mukukutu\x + 9.13. Eki. 32.9. Det. 10.16. 2 Madz. 17.14. Zvir. 29.1.\x*.
\s Vana vaIsraeri vakamukira Jehovha murenje
\p
\v 7 Rangarira, usakanganwa, kuti wakatsamwisa Jehovha Mwari wako murenje; kubva pazuva rawakabuda munyika yeEgipita kusvika masvika panzvimbo iyi manga muchimukira Jehovha\x + Eki. 14.11. 16.2. 17.2. Num. 11.4. 20.2. 25.2. Det. 31.27.\x*.
\v 8 NepaHorebhu makatsamwisa Jehovha, kusvika Jehovha akakutsamwirai kukuparadzai\x + Eki. 32.4. Map. 106.19.\x*.
\v 9 Pandaiva ndakwira mugomo kunogamuchira mahwendefa emabwe, mahwendefa esungano Jehovha yaakaita nemwi\x + Eki. 24.12,15.\x*, zvino ndakagara mugomo mazuva makumi mana neusiku makumi mana; handina kudya chingwa kana kunwa mvura\x + Eki. 24.18. 34.28.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino Jehovha wakandipa mahwendefa awa maviri emabwe akanyorwa nemunwe waMwari; uye pamusoro pawo \add pakanyorwa\add* zvemashoko ese Jehovha aakataura kwamuri mugomo ari mukati memoto\x + Eki. 31.18.\x* nezuva reungano\x + Eki. 19.17. Det. 4.10. 10.4. 18.16.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino zvakaitika pakupera kwemazuva makumi mana neusiku makumi mana, \add kuti\add* Jehovha wakandipa mahwendefa maviri emabwe, mahwendefa esungano.
\v 12 Zvino Jehovha wakati kwandiri: Simuka, buruka nekukurumidza ubve pano, nokuti vanhu vako vawakabudisa muEgipita va\add zvi\add*svibisa\x + Eki. 32.7,8.\x*; vatsauka nekukurumidza panzira yandakavaraira; vazviitira chifananidzo chakaumbwa nekunyungudusa\x + 9.16. Det. 31.29. Vato. 2.17.\x*.
\v 13 Uye Jehovha wakataura kwandiri achiti: Ndaona vanhu ava\x + Eki. 32.9.\x*, zvino tarira, vanhu vane mitsipa mikukutu\x + 9.6.\x*.
\v 14 Ndirege kuti ndivaparadze\x + Vato. 11.37. Eki. 32.10.\x*, uye ndidzime zita ravo kubva pasi pematenga\x + 29.20. 7.24.\x*; zvino ndichakuita uve rudzi rwune simba uye rwakawanda kuvapfuura\x + Num. 14.12.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino ndakatendeuka ndikaburuka mugomo\x + Eki. 32.15.\x*; gomo ndokupfuta nemoto; zvino mahwendefa maviri esungano aiva mumaoko angu maviri\x + 4.11. 5.23. Eki. 19.18.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino ndakatarira, zvino tarira, maiva matadzira Jehovha Mwari wenyu; mazviitira mhuru yakaumbwa nekunyungudusa; maiva makurumidza kutsauka kubva munzira Jehovha yaakakurairai\x + Eki. 32.19.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino ndakabata mahwendefa maviri, ndokuarasa kubva mumaoko angu, ndokuaputsa pamberi pemeso enyu.
\v 18 Zvino ndakawira pasi pameso aJehovha\x + 9.25. Eki. 34.28. Map. 106.23.\x* sepakutanga, mazuva makumi mana neusiku makumi mana\x + 9.9.\x*; handina kudya chingwa kana kunwa mvura, nekuda kwezvivi zvenyu zvose zvamakatadza pakuita zvakaipa pamberi paJehovha, muchimutsamwisa\x + 4.25.\x*.
\v 19 Nokuti ndakatya kutsamwa nekupfuta Jehovha kwaaiva akutsamwirai nako kukuparadzai; asi Jehovha wakandinzwawo panguva iyo\x + Eki. 32.10,14,33,34. 33.17. Det. 10.10.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino Jehovha waiva akatsamwirawo zvikuru Aroni kuti amuparadze; ndikanyengetererawo naAroni panguva iyo\x + Eki. 32.20.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino ndakatora chivi chenyu, mhuru yamaiva maita, ndokuipisa nemoto, ndokuipwanya, ndichiikuisisa kusvika yava diki seguruva; zvino ndakakandira guruva rayo murukova rwaiburuka kubva mugomo.
\v 22 NepaTabhera\x + Num. 11.1,3.\x* nepaMasa\x + Eki. 17.7.\x* nepaKibhuroti-Hatava\x + Num. 11.4,34.\x* maitsamwisa Jehovha.
\v 23 Neapo Jehovha paakutumai kubva paKadheshi-Bharineya\x + Num. 13.3,26; 14.1.\x*, achiti: Kwirai mugare nhaka yenyika yandakakupai, zvino makamukira murairo waJehovha Mwari wenyu, uye hamuna kumutenda kana kuteerera kuinzwi rake\x + Map. 106.24,25.\x*.
\v 24 Maiva vanomukira Jehovha kubva pazuva rekukuzivai kwangu\x + 9.7. Det. 31.27.\x*.
\v 25 Zvino ndakazviwisira pasi pamberi paJehovha mazuva makumi mana neusiku makumi mana, andakazviwisira pasi nawo\x + 9.18.\x*; nokuti Jehovha waiva ati achakuparadzai.
\v 26 Zvino ndakanyengetera kuna Jehovha ndokuti: Ishe Jehovha, musaparadza vanhu venyu nenhaka yenyu, vamakadzikunura neukuru hwenyu, vamakabudisa kubva muEgipita neruoko rwune simba\x + Eki. 32.11-13.\x*.
\v 27 Rangarirai varanda venyu, Abhurahama, Isaka, naJakove; musatarisa nharo dzevanhu ava nekuipa kwavo nechivi chavo;
\v 28 zvimwe nyika yamakatibudisa mairi iti: Nekuda kwekuti Jehovha waiva asingakwanisi kuvapinza munyika yaakavavimbisa, uye nokuti waiva achivavenga, wakavabudisa kuti avauraire murenje\x + Num. 14.16.\x*.
\v 29 Ivo vanhu venyu uye nhaka yenyu, vamakabudisa nesimba renyu guru uye neruoko rwenyu rwakatandavadzwa\x + 1 Madz. 8.51. Neh. 1.10. Det. 4.20.\x*.